              style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: normal; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif-light, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">感じる</em>ようになるのです。」（「<a
              class="cross-ref" href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/general-conference/2000/10/now-is-the-time?lang=jpn&amp;para=9#p9"
