              style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: normal; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif-light, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">『リアホナ』</cite>2001年1月号，89）</mark></span></p>
